			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "The smallest chest. Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"Well, you wanted a bigger chest. Now you have it. The Draconic Chest is the biggest chest you'll get in this pack."
				""
				"The Draconic Chest is a high capacity chest with a built-in crafting table and an auto-smelting furnace. It can store up to 234 stacks of items and has an internal energy buffer of 1,000,000 RF to power the smelting process."
			]
			dependencies: [
				"212CBE2DA076A4E3"
				"12AC8B789FF3D939"
